Silverlight</link> <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2213%22])">13</ref> . Liberty spends his time creating videos, tutorials, showcase applications, and speaking at industry events <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%2214%22])">14</ref></p>
